Description: RDE (Ruizi Desktop Environment) - Web-based Desktop for Linux Servers
 RDE is an open-source web desktop environment that turns Linux servers
 into feature-rich cloud desktops with a Windows-like browser experience.
 .
 Features:
  - File Manager: upload, download, preview, share with TUS resumable uploads
  - Docker Apps: visual container/image management, one-click deploy
  - Download Manager: aria2-based HTTP/BT/magnet download management
  - Samba Sharing: LAN file sharing service
  - File Sync: Syncthing multi-device sync
  - System Monitor: real-time CPU, memory, disk, network dashboard
  - Backup & Restore: local, WebDAV, S3, SFTP backup targets
  - Web Terminal: full-featured terminal in the browser
  - Plugin System: extend with premium features via plugins
